        " رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"كِيلُوا طَعَامَكُمْ فَإِنَّ اَلْبَرَكَةَ فِي اَلطَّعَامِ اَلْمَكِيلِ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3965 - The Messenger of Allah (swt), peace be upon him and his family, said:\n\"Measure your food, for indeed, the blessing is in the measured food.\""
